==Swedish==

===Alternative spellings===
* [[mänska]]

===Noun===
{{sv-noun-reg-or|människ}}
# [[human being]]; mostly hairless [[primate]] of the genus [[w:Homo (genus)|Homo]]; especially species [[w:Homo sapiens|Homo sapiens]]
# [[person]], [[people]]; (''as a count'')
#: ''Tre '''människor''' skadades i olyckan'' = ''Three '''persons''' were injured in the accident.''

===Synonyms===
* [[Homo sapiens]]

